Rails 3.1 assets inspiration: https://gist.github.com/923998

Automated JS testing reference: https://gist.github.com/673967


Integrated so far (all about buzzwords):

- Rspec
- Autotest
- Sprockets
- coffeescript
- jasmine
- guard
- mongoid


How to run:
- git clone
- bundle install
- bundle exec rake jasmine
- guard
- autotest (no ruby specs so far)


